result.title: TLE due to #define macro
result.content:
In the recent codeforces round 446 div 2. Link below. http://codeforces.com/contest/892/problem/B

I got a TLE in my code in pretest 9. code link below. http://codeforces.com/contest/892/submission/32424091

but when I removed one of the #define macro. my code got accepted. Link below. http://codeforces.com/contest/892/submission/32424097

Can someone explain the reason for getting TLE.
